'''Banque Populaire du Rwanda Public Limited Company''' ('''BPR PLC'''; ),Yahoze ari  '''Banque Populaire du Rwanda SA''', Ni Banki y'ubucuruzi ikorera mu rwanda kuva muri 1975. BPR yemewe na banki nkuru y'u Rwanda kandi ikurikiza amategeko agenga izindi banki mu gihugu.<ref>https://www.bpr.rw/</ref>

== Incamake ==
BPR ni banki icuruza , itanga konti zo kuzigama no gukoresha bisanzwe, amakarita yo kubikuza no kuguriza,  hamwe ninguzanyo. Banki itanga ibikoresho bya banki byabaguzi nka banki igendanwa muri telefone. <ref name="3R">https://www.rwandayp.com/company/2507/Banque_Populaire</ref>


Muri 2016, BPR yakoresheje abakozi bagera kuri 1.400 icyo gihe. <ref name="4R">https://rw.kcbgroup.com/about-us/news-room/banking/kcb-group-plc-completes-acquisition-of-banque-populaire-du-rwanda-plc-bpr</ref> Ariko, nyuma yo kugurwa na Atlas Mara, hamwe no guhuza ubucuruzi na BRD, abantu bagera kuri 300 barahagaritswe. <ref name="5R">http://en.igihe.com/business/article/kcb-group-completes-acquisition-of-banque-populaire-du-rwanda</ref>

== Amateka ==
Inkomoko ya banki irashobora guhera mu 1975, igihe Banque Populaire du Rwanda ya mbere yashingwaga mu mudugudu wa Nkamba, mu mujyi wa Kibungo, [[Intara y’Iburasirazuba|Intara y'Iburasirazuba]] . Mu myaka icumi yakurikiyeho, andi mabanki menshi asa nayo yashinzwe hirya no hino. Mu 1986, Banques zitandukanye zigenga zashizeho umutaka witwa Union des Banques Populaires du Rwanda (UBPR). UBPR yakoraga nka banki ya koperative. 

Muri Mutarama 2008, nyuma y’imyaka 33 y’uburambe mu rwego rw’imari y’u Rwanda, UBPR yahinduwe ivuye muri banki y’amakoperative ihinduka banki y’ubucuruzi: Banque Populaire du Rwanda SA <ref name="6R">https://en.igihe.com/business/article/banque-populaire-du-rwanda-plc-announces-changes-in-its-personal-banking-loan</ref> Muri Kamena 2008, Rabobank, ihuriro ry’amabanki y’amakoperative y’Ubuholandi, yaguze 35% y'imigabane muri BPR. <ref name="7R">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/business/bpr-reports-rwf38bn-after-tax-profit-2020</ref> Muri Nyakanga 2012, Visa Inc. yemeje ko banki itanga amakarita yo kubikuza hamwe n'amakarita y'inguzanyo. <ref name="8R">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/188468</ref>

Muri Mutarama 2016, Atlas Mara yarangije kugura imigabane igenzura BPR nyuma yo kubona imigabane ku banyamigabane bariho <ref name="9R">https://africa.businessinsider.com/local/markets/rwanda-approves-purchase-of-banque-populaire-du-rwanda-by-kcb/k8sexy2</ref> no guhuza banki n’ubucuruzi bw’amabanki y’ubucuruzi bwahagaritse Banki y’iterambere ry’u Rwanda  BRD. <ref name="10R">https://eng.inyarwanda.com/inkuru/63344/atlas-mara-in-deal-to-buy-rwandan-bank-63344.html</ref>

Muri Mata 2019, Itsinda rya Equity Bank Group, ihuriro rya kabiri mu masosiyete manini muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba, ryashyize ahagaragara gahunda yo kugura 62% bya Banque Populaire du Rwanda, mu kugabana imigabane na Atlas Mara Limited . <ref name="11R">https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/78404/banki-y-abaturage-78404.html</ref>

