== Umuyoboro w'ishami ==
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2019, Banki Populaire du Rwanda yagumanye umuyoboro w’amashami agera kuri 200 yuzuye, hamwe na ATM zirenga 100 mu [[Rwanda|turere twose two mu Rwanda]] .  <ref name="13R">https://ar.umuseke.rw/banque-populaire-na-brd-zaba-zigiye-guhuzwa-zikaba-banki-imwe.hmtl</ref> <ref name="14R">http://www.en.umuseke.rw/bpr-bank-robbery-in-ruhango-distinct.html</ref>

== Imiyoborere ==
Ibikorwa bya Banque Populaire du Rwanda bigenzurwa ninama yubuyobozi yabantu icyenda ihagarariye ibikorwa byubucuruzi, imishinga, ibyago hamwe numuyoboro wishami, iyobowe numuyobozi mukuru. Umuyobozi mukuru uriho ubu ni Maurice Toroitich. <ref name="15R">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/featured-banque-populaire-du-rwanda-opens-two-new-branches</ref> Umuyobozi w'inama y'ubutegetsi ni Njuguna Ndung'u . <ref name="16R">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/222799</ref> Ibikorwa bya buri munsi bya banki bicungwa nitsinda ryabanyamuryango icumi, riyobowe numuyobozi mukuru, Maurice Toroitich. 

